description.displayText:
She's considerate and cares about the kids not only being safe but also having fun. She's one of the few babysitters we had that actually cleaned up after the kids. She's always on time or in touch about her schedule. Nothing seems to faze her when it comes to dealing with kids.

She's more mature than her age suggests. Our kids loved her and she related to an 11 year old boy and 3 year old girl with ease and grace. A family would be lucky to have her be a part of their lives.

description.displayText: Leanna has been a regular babysitter for our family for about 2 years. She is incredibly warm and fun and creative and the kids LOVE when she comes over. She is very responsible and has never been late or missed an appointment. I do not hesitate at all to recommend her as a babysitter for other families. You will be lucky to work with her!
